room_title: Escape room "Return To Planet Earth Junior" by Code Breakers in Pittsburgh
room_description:
You are trapped aboard an alien spacecraft in the deep reaches of space. This spacecraft is far from functional, and there's no one to pilot it anyway - or is there? You and your team must return the spacecraft to working order, learn how to operate it and, if you have what it takes, Return to Planet Earth...
This is the kids version of our popular Return To Planet Earth experience.
